      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEEN OF SEES (4) is a lightly-raced but progressive filly who is two for two so far this campaign. Came from one spot wider than this to win the Graduation Series 3YO Trot Final at Maryborough last time. Talented and can continue to work through her grades. KISS AT MIDNIGHT (6) kept her manners in check and showed what she is capable of when leading to score by 4.7m at Geelong last week. Draws wider but has won here before. HILLWINSOME (2) has had seven weeks off but he draws well and his form is consistent, recording a string of top-four results since a win at this venue. Go well. EL TORNADO (1) has made mistakes in both starts since a spell but gets the ace draw and won his lone third-up attempt so could be a big improver with manners.",
